data.description: Escape to tranquil country living with this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a picturesque 2.5-acre lot in Quincy. This property offers a perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and rustic charm, surrounded by natural beauty and expansive outdoor space. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious entryway featuring a large wall built-in for convenient storage of shoes and jackets, keeping everything organized and tidy. The primary bedroom boasts its own attached bathroom for added privacy and convenience. Throughout the home, you'll find touches of rustic charm that enhance the cozy atmosphere. Stay warm and cozy on chilly nights with the pellet stove, which efficiently takes the chill off.  All-new windows throughout the house not only enhance energy efficiency but also allow ample natural light to illuminate the living spaces. Outside, the property offers ample storage with two storage sheds and a large, oversized garage measuring 24 x 48, perfect for storing vehicles, equipment, and more. The back patio is a true oasis, featuring a hot tub and a pergola providing shade and a relaxing ambiance - ideal for winding or entertaining friends and family.  Located in a serene country setting, yet within easy reach of Quincy amenities and services, this home offers the best of both worlds.  This company makes no warranty or representations about the contents of this data. It is the responsibility of the parties looking at the property to satisfy themselves as to accuracy of this information. Taxes were obtained from the local assessor and the taxes could change for the buyer after a closed transaction.
